message.content: cs.SE, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.PL, cs.ET - This paper discusses the limitations of the IEC 61131 standard and proposes the IEC 61499 standard as a solution for complex industrial systems. This topic falls under the scope of software engineering (cs.SE), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), programming languages (cs.PL), and embedded systems (cs.ET).
